`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- The state machine uses **immutable updates** (returning new objects, never mutating) — this matches the pure function pattern established in `questChainEngine.ts` and makes tests deterministic.
- Guard conditions (`if state !== "active" return same ref`) let tests verify no-op cases with `toBe(quest)` identity checks — a stronger assertion than deep equality.
